commit.message:
re PR bootstrap/12383 (Bootstrap fails in dwarf2out with `HAVE_GAS_SHF_MERGE' undeclared)

2003-09-23  Andrew Pinski  <apinski@apple.com>

        PR bootstrap/12383
        * configure: Regenerate.

From-SVN: r71721

files.patch:

+
+	PR bootstrap/12383
+	* configure: Regenerate.
+
 2003-09-23  Nathanael Nerode  <neroden@gcc.gnu.org>
